OL,3,CMum pays nearly #3,000 for son's
OL,4,Cautism referral after 4 year wait
OL,6,FWATCH: A mother from Kent tells ITV
OL,7,FMeridian's how she paid thousands for
OL,8,Fa referral for her son.
OL,10,FA mother from Kent has paid nearly
OL,11,F#3,000 for her son to have a referral
OL,12,Ffor an autism assessment, after
OL,13,Fwaiting four and a half years on the
OL,14,FNHS.
OL,16,FHayley Vannerley first noticed her son
OL,17,FReuben's severe mood swings and
OL,18,Finattentive behaviour when he was in
OL,19,Fnursery in Faversham, which only
OL,20,Fworsened at school.
