OL,3,CMum pays nearly #3,000 for son's
OL,4,Cautism referral after 4 year wait
OL,6,FReuben was finally diagnosed with
OL,7,Fautism and ADHD in November last year,
OL,8,Fafter a wait which Hayley says left
OL,9,Fher son feeling suicidal.
OL,11,FHayley said: "You shouldn't have to
OL,12,Fpay for it, but when you're backed
OL,13,Finto a corner, you only want the best
OL,14,Ffor your child.
OL,16,F"He needed the help, so the only
OL,17,Foption we had was to pay privately.
OL,18,FWithin 10 weeks, he had a
OL,19,Fdiagnosis...and that got the ball
OL,20,Frolling.
