OL,6,F"Everything was in place for school
OL,7,Fand all of his needs were met. It was
OL,8,Fa massive turning point."
OL,10,FAn avalanche of demand for autism and
OL,11,FADHD services has created an
OL,12,Fescalating crisis for the NHS in the
OL,13,Fsouth east, new analysis suggests.
OL,15,FResearch by the health think-tank, the
OL,16,FNuffield Trust, reveals an
OL,17,F'extraordinary' rise in demand for
OL,18,Fautism assessments and ADHD treatments.
