OL,6,FThea Stein, Chief Executive of the
OL,7,FNuffield Trust said: "I think that
OL,8,Fwe're at a tipping point and an
OL,9,Finteresting point as a society,
OL,10,Fdefinitely.
OL,12,F"What we are going to need to see is
OL,13,Fall workplaces, all educational
OL,14,Fsettings to understand something that
OL,15,Factually should feel quite normal,
OL,16,Fthat we're all different, that we all
OL,17,Flearn differently, that we all
OL,18,Fexperience the world differently.
