OL,6,F"So I think we will we will hopefully
OL,7,Fbecome a society that is more
OL,8,Finterested, tolerant, open and
OL,9,Faccepting of the diversity that we
OL,10,Fhave.
OL,12,F"Then we will be able to use our
OL,13,Fservices in a focused way for those
OL,14,Fpeople. We really have very, very
OL,15,Fserious and very complex neurodiverse
OL,16,Fproblems."
