OL,6,FLatest figures show, in Kent and
OL,7,FMedway, there are 7225 patients
OL,8,Fwaiting for an assessment. Of this,
OL,9,F6090 have been on a waiting list for
OL,10,Fmore than three months already.
OL,12,FWhile in Sussex, 4980 are on the
OL,13,Fwaiting list, while 4400 people have
OL,14,Fbeen waiting more than 13 weeks to be
OL,15,Fassessed for autism, according to NHS
OL,16,Fdata from December 2023.
