OL,6,FA spokesperson for NHS Kent and Medway
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are sorry families are
OL,8,Fwaiting longer than we would like them
OL,9,Fto for an assessment for either ASD or
OL,10,FADHD, we appreciate how frustrating
OL,11,Fthis can be.
OL,13,F"There has been a significant rise in
OL,14,Fdemand for these assessments since the
OL,15,Fpandemic.
OL,17,F"The NHS and our partners are working
OL,18,Fhard to make sure the right support is
OL,19,Favailable to families, with or without
OL,20,Fan assessment, as this is important
OL,21,Ffor all children and young people."
